		<div id="comment_body_64392634"><p>Nope. The robots will be replicated if they accomplish their mission, not for mere survival.</p><p>Compare kamikaze pilots to cruise missiles:</p><p>Kamikaze pilot X is a hero. He completes his mission and dies. Kamikaze pilot Y is a coward. He chickens out and runs away before his turn to fly.</p><p>Result: X is a genetic dead end, while Y goes on to have children and grandchildren.</p><p>Cruise missile X launches and destroys its target. Cruise missile Y malfunctions and fails to launch.</p><p>Result: More model X missiles are manufactured<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

